# Project Overview

Vue 3 + .NET 9 monorepo. **Aspire AppHost is the default dev entry point.**

## Layout

```
vue-shadcn-template/
├── apps/web/          # Vue 3 + Vite + shadcn-vue + Effect API client
├── apps/api/          # .NET 9 Web API (JWT auth, EF Core, OpenAPI/Scalar)
├── apps/api.tests/    # xUnit integration tests
├── aspire/
│   ├── AppHost/       # DistributedApplication orchestration
│   └── ServiceDefaults/
├── e2e/               # Playwright (starts api + web)
└── Template.sln
```

## Stack

| Layer | Tech |
|-------|------|
| Frontend | Vue 3, Pinia, Vue Router, Tailwind 4, shadcn-vue, **Effect** + `fetch` |
| Backend | .NET 9, EF Core migrations, JWT, Scalar (dev) |
| Orchestration | .NET Aspire AppHost |
| Tests | Vitest (web), xUnit (api), Playwright (e2e) |

## Auth

All CRUD routes inherit `[Authorize]` from `BaseController<T>`. Auth endpoints live at `api/auth/*`. Frontend guards routes with `meta.requiresAuth` / `meta.guest`.

## Dev workflow

```bash
# Preferred
dotnet run --project aspire/AppHost

# Or standalone
dotnet run --project apps/api
cd apps/web && npm run dev
```

